vote.title: Authorize a three-year lease agreement with 2722 Burbank, LLC, for approximately 8,371 square feet of office and warehouse space located at 2734 Burbank Street, to be used for the Emergency Services Division of the Dallas Fire-Rescue Department for the period March 1, 2023 through February 28, 2026 - Not to exceed $457,799.30 - Financing: General Fund (subject to annual appropriations) (see Fiscal Information)
